1. Open Web Console

2. Create a file "testing.sh" using nano or vi editor
	 #!/bin/bash
	 echo "Wel to Shell Script Example"
	
3. Run "testing.sh"
	 /bin/bash testing.sh
	
4. Copy "testing.sh" in your home directory in hdfs	
	 hadoop fs -copyFromLocal testing.sh
	
5. Go to Hue and create new Workflow
	 Rename "My Workflow"
	 Drag "Shell Action" and select the path of testing.sh
	 Note: testing.sh path should choose in File path also
	
6. Save and Submit the workflow
